{"tid":517036,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港股戰報】恒指穿三萬創逾十年高！專家：升幅有啲唔合理","createTime":"2018-01-02T02:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T03:47:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"64ce8f2de7f632edd0ace246a2ae78a698e71302","tid":517036,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180102/large/1514856435_d5c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180102%2Flarge%2F1514856435_d5c8.jpg&h=8c0eeb90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港股在2018年首個交易日一舉升穿三萬，在高開逾百點之下，恒指開報30,028點，其後升幅進一步擴大，最新報30,348點，升426點，為07年11月以來高；H指最新升264點，報11,973點，暫錄得成交302.26億元。<br />\n<br />\n推動大市升幅仍然是騰訊（700），最新升逾2%，報414.6元；其次是建行（939）升近2%，報7.34元；滙控（005）亦升1%，報80.9元。手機設備股造好，舜宇（2382）再升穿100元關，報102.2元；九倉（004）亦升逾1%，報27.3元。友邦（1299）升近1%，報67.25元。<br />\n<br />\n但濠賭股受壓，銀娛（27）跌5.4%，報59.3元；永利澳門（1128）跌5.66%，報23.35元。合和（54）悉售合和基建（737），合和最新升一成，報31.95元；合和基建則要跌3%，報4.83元。<br />\n宏滙資產管理董事及投資策略總監林嘉麒認為，今日升幅不太合理，A股開盤不太差，所以有少少「博亂」，短期有力彈上，一周目標30,0500點，支持位是30,000點，如果守得住，指數會慢慢向上。"},{"pid":"1cbe79de90723d85739472dda0521d3ada228063","tid":517036,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171226/large/1514295329_8a36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171226%2Flarge%2F1514295329_8a36.jpg&h=08216203&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90f8a3d4aaa23c23ee0ad762634e5a52231d1001","tid":517036,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:33:01.000Z","msg":"專家話股巿轉淡，你要快快斬倉"},{"pid":"a6f1e3c00bd5466ccbabcd23c971c92ed1e414d8","tid":517036,"uid":124410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:33:54.000Z","msg":"個專家未有貨佢未話唔合理囉<br />\non9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=